nd gold of the Games.\", \"from\": 1028, \"to\": 1115, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1054, \"end\": 1063, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\", \"score\": 0.9999303028859378, \"rank\": 6.954195756576734e-05, \"text\": \"BBC Sport\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\"}, {\"begin\": 1080, \"end\": 1087, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9999942946364129, \"rank\": 3.5718356229939594e-06, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an emotional Pidcock\", \"from\": 1028, \"to\": 1048}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 1105, \"to\": 1114}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I think the Olympics is so special and I think it's just\\u2026 you never give up, you give everything and that's what I had to do.'\", \"from\": 1117, \"to\": 1244, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1126, \"to\": 1138}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 1204, \"to\": 1214}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Pidcock's decisive, high-risk overtake of Koretzky appeared to upset many of the onlooking French fans, who booed the British cyclist as he romped home in first.\", \"from\": 1246, \"to\": 1407, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1337, \"end\": 1343, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\", \"score\": 0.9595292789892161, \"rank\": 0.03831907789320607, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\"}, {\"begin\": 1364, \"end\": 1371, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Boxing_Board_of_Control\", \"score\": 0.7331527043440346, \"rank\": 0.2394236159144851, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Boxing_Board_of_Control\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Boxing_Board_of_Control\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Pidcock's decisive, high-risk overtake\", \"from\": 1246, \"to\": 1284}, {\"ngram\": \"Koretzky\", \"from\": 1288, \"to\": 1296}, {\"ngram\": \"home\", \"from\": 1393, \"to\": 1397}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I knew Victor was going to be super fast on the last lap and I could not get rid of him so I knew it was going to be a big, big fight,' Pidcock added.\", \"from\": 1409, \"to\": 1560, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1417, \"end\": 1423, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Victor_Newman\", \"score\": 0.5565407774756919, \"rank\": 0.7967121501921035, \"text\": \"Victor\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Victor_Newman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Victor_Newman\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the last lap\", \"from\": 1454, \"to\": 1466}, {\"ngram\": \"a big, big fight\", \"from\": 1527, \"to\": 1543}, {\"ngram\": \"Pidcock\", \"from\": 1546, \"to\": 1553}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'He left a gap and I had to go for it so that's racing.\", \"from\": 1562, \"to\": 1617, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a gap\", \"from\": 1571, \"to\": 1576}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Some people might view it differently.\", \"from\": 1618, \"to\": 1656, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Some people\", \"from\": 1618, \"to\": 1629}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I wanted to show what the sport is, not giving up.\", \"from\": 1658, \"to\": 1709, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 1681, \"to\": 1690}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's a shame the French were booing me, but you know.'\", \"from\": 1710, \"to\": 1764, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1727, \"end\": 1733, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\", \"score\": 0.9595292789892161, \"rank\": 0.03831907789320607, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"h